<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Meadowlark Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">As of 2006, 96.1% of the Meadowlark real estate is made up of detached single-family homes (bungalow and two storey), with the remaining 3.9% being apartments. 17.3% of the homes are used for rental purposes.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Anchored by The Bay, two new anchors, Nordstrom and Target, are to be added to replace Sears and Zellers respectively</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Meadowlark Park is located in Ward 11 and represented by Brian Pincott on the Calgary City Council</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Provincially, Meadowlark Park is located in the Calgary-Elbow riding, represented by Alison Redford, current Premier of Alberta and federally in the Calgary Centre riding, currently without representation after the resignation of Lee Richardson.</p>
        </div>
